                <title>If emphasizing work and original author</title>
                <p><red>Author last name, first name.</red> <lightblue>Title of work.</lightblue> Translated by Translator first name last name, <purple>Publisher,</purple> <lightgreen>Date of publication.</lightgreen></p>
