            <example>
                <title>If emphasizing translation and translator (less common, and only if translation itself is being examined)</title>
                <p>Translator last name, first name, translator. <lightblue>Title of work.</lightblue> By <red>Author first name last name,</red> <purple>Publisher,</purple> <lightgreen>Date.</lightgreen></p>
